name: Music Collection Completer
tagline: Designed for people have large collections of albums, this is a Windows app that analyses your music collection and tells you which albums you are missing.
body:
Get started
-----------

[Download version 1.0 here](https://github.com/danielflower/MusicCollectionCompleter/releases/download/v1.0/MusicCollectionCompleter-1.0.zip) and unzip to any folder on your computer. Then just run `MusicCollectionCompleter.exe`

Note: Windows support only. [See all releases.](https://github.com/danielflower/MusicCollectionCompleter/releases)
